    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137930/extras/ce8a95ff5ff0e30bd823457a8b39206b.poster.avif?t=1733593761\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137930/extras/ce8a95ff5ff0e30bd823457a8b39206b.webm?t=1733593761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137930/extras/ce8a95ff5ff0e30bd823457a8b39206b.mp4?t=1733593761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >IMPETUM - thriller with elements of detective fiction, drama, and horror.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137930/extras/3f75289f3d0aac58d5ed7945157fc485.poster.avif?t=1733593761\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137930/extras/3f75289f3d0aac58d5ed7945157fc485.webm?t=1733593761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137930/extras/3f75289f3d0aac58d5ed7945157fc485.mp4?t=1733593761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The main character returns home from a long business trip, where his wife and young son eagerly await him. However, upon his arrival, he discovers that something is amiss: the house feels strangely empty, and an unnatural silence pervades the air.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137930/extras/bfe67284cef500953877428a947e95eb.poster.avif?t=1733593761\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137930/extras/bfe67284cef500953877428a947e95eb.webm?t=1733593761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137930/extras/bfe67284cef500953877428a947e95eb.mp4?t=1733593761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Soon, he becomes entangled in a series of mystical and inexplicable events, delving deeper into mysteries that make him question the reality of what is happening. Can he unravel these enigmas and find his family?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game Features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Realistic graphics</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Frightening atmosphere</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Tense sound design</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Intriguing storyline</p>",
